    <mxCell id="sum" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fef3c7;strokeColor=#b45309;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacingLeft=10;spacingRight=10;" value="&lt;b&gt;blocktiling&lt;/b&gt; (kernels 3-6): a &lt;b&gt;block&lt;/b&gt; → BM×BN tile in SMEM, K chunked by BK.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;threadtiling&lt;/b&gt; (kernels 4-6): a &lt;b&gt;thread&lt;/b&gt; → TM×TN patch in registers.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;b style=&quot;color:#2563eb&quot;&gt;warptiling&lt;/b&gt; (kernel 10) inserts a &lt;b&gt;warp&lt;/b&gt; → WM×WN level between them, matching the SM sub-partition that schedules each warp." vertex="1"><mxGeometry x="20" y="300" width="950" height="46" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
